(secondQuint)Evaluation of the Agili-C Biphasic Implant in the Knee Joint.

 Agili-C implant is a bi-phasic, porous resorbable tissue regeneration scaffold for the treatment of focal articular cartilage and for osteochondral defects.

 Up to 50 patients are to be included in the study.

 Patients suffering from isolated, single and focal cartilage or osteochondral defect at the knee joint are considered for study inclusion.

